title: Emperor-in-Law
alternative_titles: Son in Law of The Emperor
summary: Emperor-in-Law ManhuaAn ordinary self-funded university student suddenly acquires a rich, mature wife and activates the ‘Life Decision System.’ Does this system provide options that will become reality upon choosing them? Little children make choices; I want everything! Find out how Lifan, the son-in-law of a wealthy family, counterattacks little by little with the system in hand to become this generation’s greatest son-in-law! Emperor Son In Law Son in Law of The Emperor 帝婿
